<para style="p">For the chief musician; set to Shoshannim. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Save me, God;</para>

<para style="q1">for the waters have put my life in danger.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />I sink in deep mire, where there is no place to stand;</para>

<para style="q1">I have come into deep waters, where the floods flow over me.</para>
